  "title": "Cook",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>• Prepare and cook minced meat noodles, soup, and related\nmenu items.</p><p>• Ensure food quality, taste, and presentation meet company\nstandards.</p><p>• Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of the kitchen and stall.</p><p>• Assist with ingredient preparation, stock management, and\ndaily operations.</p><p>• Follow food safety and workplace safety guidelines.<br /></p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><p>• Prior cooking experience preferred, but no experience is\nalso welcome – training will be provided.</p><p>• Familiar with or able to learn how to cook minced meat\nnoodles.</p><p>• Able to work in a fast-paced environment.</p><p>• Team player with good communication skills.</p><p>• Willing to work shifts, weekends, and public holidays.</p>",
